    </div>

    <p>The gummy format has made lion's mane supplementation significantly more accessible to mainstream consumers. For a comprehensive ranking of every cognitive-support gummy — including multi-ingredient nootropic stacks — see our guide to the <a href="/best-brain-gummies/">best brain gummies</a>. For the full science behind NGF stimulation, neuroprotection, and the clinical trials on memory and focus, read our deep dive on <a href="/blog/what-does-lions-mane-do/">what does lion's mane do</a>. However, not all lion's mane gummies are created equal. The critical differentiator is whether the product uses fruiting body extract (high in bioactive compounds) or mycelium-on-grain (diluted with starch filler). Understanding this distinction is essential for choosing a product that actually works.</p>

    <div class="info-cards">
